# design_loop.evaluate appends to <model>.history.jsonl on every call,
# including from the test suite. These are test side-effects, not
# engineering history — in production they should be archived externally
# (e.g. an append-only log shipped to a data lake) rather than committed
# to source control.
*.history.jsonl
